\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242166 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid854880\charrsid11011264 Do you know how old your mother was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12287980 FE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid854880\charrsid11011264 Well she was pre
tty young - I'm not sure. My mother came from Ball. My mother comes from very old family and I've got the history of my mother dating back to 1832. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16650296\charrsid11011264 
I've got a - a record of the family tree and it\rquote s very, very interesting. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid854880\charrsid11011264 And I was first given this history by somebody from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
