\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16650296\charrsid11011264 Bobby}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid854880\charrsid11011264  lives there, the baker now. And I remember well my brother and me fighting on top of {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Station Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, and someone came down to tell my father. And he took hold of my hair and marched me up to the attic you see, in jail. And I'd only been there two minutes and I went out through the skylight and I walked along the gutter and over the bit where the }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16650296\charrsid11011264 bake house}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid854880\charrsid11011264  is now. I was playing in the top of {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}
